Egypt, Burundi, Libya, Seychelles, Sudan, and Tanzania are yet to confirm participation in the women's category while Burundi, Libya, Sudan, and Tanzania, have not confirmed in men's categoryKenya Hockey Union (KHU) secretary general Wycliffe Ongori said the union expects Kenya coaches to whittle down their squads by next weekOngori at the same time said they are engaging a leading media company to broadcast the seven-day event